description: Quentin Gainz is in need of a rub down from his head down to his toes (and all points in between), and Dalton Riley is just the man for the job. Dalton's special technique is sure to loosen Quentin up, and though he may feel a little stiffness during the session, Dalton assures Quentin will be satisfied with the release in the outcome. Quentin admits Dalton's methods are somewhat peculiar, but once Dalton touches him, he realizes he's in good hands. Sure enough, Dalton hits all of Quentin's spots and Quentin admits that this is just the the sort of hard medicine he's been missing in his life.Enjoy!
title: Fucking Massage
